  • public class NormalizedPercentagesColumn
extends AmpDifferentialColumn<PercentageTextCell>
    a column which fetches items with percentages from a view with a "nonNulls" column and associated PercentagesCorrector instance. PercentagesCorrector is used for correcting dirty AMP data (e.g. where percentages for a given activity id do not add up to 100%)
